message.body: And would love to see you if you have time for something quick?
Welcome back!! My friend Julia is having a brunch at her apartment near Coolidge corner in Brookline around noon-- want to come? Ill send you the address
Ill call you when I'm headed over, and hopefully we can coordinate! But no worries if not :) miss you love you!
Katya I'm sorry. I can't go. I'm too intimidated by my homework to leave it alone. I'm lame. Don't take it personally
Aw that's too bad. Come one! Are you sure?
Don't you live near Coolidge corner? If you're really stressed though, no worries
